Package: transportation.gov
Title: US Department of Transportation Open Data Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for data.transportation.gov via Socrata SODA API.
    160 cataloged datasets covering NHTSA recalls, railroad safety (FRA), transit (NTD/FTA),
    aviation (BTS), border crossings, supply chain/freight, highway statistics, motor fuel,
    driver licensing, vehicle registrations, bikeshare, maritime, and transportation economics.
    Full SoQL query support with pagination.
